text: Matt or Matthew Hughes may refer to: * Matt Hughes (actor) (born 1987), British Porn actor * Matt Hughes (writer) (born 1949), Canadian science fiction writer * Matthew Hughes (politician) (born 1950), Western Australian state politician * Matt Hughes (fighter) (born 1973), American professional mixed martial artist * Matt Hughes (rower) (born 1981), American Olympic rower * Matthew Hughes (runner) (born 1989), Canadian athlete * Matthew Hughes (cricketer) (born 1996), English cricketer ==See also== * Mathew Hughes (1822–1882), Victoria Cross recipient * Hughes (surname)
title: Matt Hughes
